                            <comment id="86357" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 11 Jun 2014 19:40:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems I never got around to cleaning that up in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3963&quot; title=&quot;cleanup libcfs wrappers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3963&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3963&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Also we need more fixes in a few other places as well in all the branches. Also is their a wrapper to change the umask value?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
